In a recent heartwarming interview hosted by @salilacharya Mr. Salil Acharya, Lakmé Academy Gandhi Nagar's Managing Director, @navneet24kukreja Mrs. Navneet Kukreja, engaged in a soulful conversation with Rishav—a remarkable 22-year-old alumnus of Lakmé Academy Gandhi Nagar who defies the odds as a deaf and mute individual.

This emotionally charged episode is a testament to Rishav's journey and triumphs in the beauty industry, showcasing the inclusive and empowering environment fostered by Lakmé Academy. Mrs. Navneet Kukreja, with her visionary leadership, shares insights into Lakmé Academy's commitment to providing opportunities for individuals from all walks of life.

Tune in for an emotional rollercoaster, brimming with inspiration, as Rishav narrates his experiences and milestones since graduating from Lakmé Academy Gandhi Nagar. For those aspiring to step into the beauty industry, this interview is a beacon of hope, proving that passion and determination know no barriers.

Catch this captivating episode, where beauty transcends boundaries, only at Lakmé Academy—Your Gateway to Inclusive Excellence! 💄🌈
